node_modules/
dist/
data/
*.log
Both parties lock a bond (separate hold invoices)
    ↓
Hunter delivers actual data (torrent seeding / file transfer)
    ↓
Payer downloads and verifies the file hash matches the torrent's piece hashes
    ↓
If delivery correct: reward escrow settled (hunter gets paid), both bonds cancelled (returned)
If hunter cheats:    reward escrow cancelled (payer refunded), hunter's bond slashed (payer keeps it)
If payer cheats:     reward escrow settled (hunter gets paid), payer's bond slashed (hunter keeps it)